[[扇形地形|扇形地形]]常见于火星南北45度到60度之间的中纬度地区，其中在北半球的乌托邦平原地区<ref name=ref1>{{cite journal | last1=Lefort | first1=A. | last2=Russell | first2=P. S. | last3=Thomas | first3=N. | last4=McEwen | first4=A. S. | last5=Dundas | first5=C. M. | last6=Kirk | first6=R. L. | title=Observations of periglacial landforms in Utopia Planitia with the High Resolution Imaging Science Experiment (HiRISE) | journal=Journal of Geophysical Research | volume=114 | issue=E4 | year=2009 | pages=E04005 | doi=10.1029/2008JE003264 | bibcode=2009JGRE..114.4005L | url=https://boris.unibe.ch/36929/ | access-date=2022-04-01 | archive-date=2021-12-10 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211210010734/https://boris.unibe.ch/36929/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Morgenstern|first1=A|last2=Hauber|first2=E|last3=Reiss|first3=D|last4=van Gasselt|first4=S|last5=Grosse|first5=G|last6=Schirrmeister|first6=L|year=2007|title=Deposition and degradation of a volatile-rich layer in Utopia Planitia, and implications for climate history on Mars|url=https://epic.awi.de/id/eprint/16592/1/Mor2007e.pdf|journal=Journal of Geophysical Research: Planets|volume=112|issue=E6|page=E06010|doi=10.1029/2006JE002869|bibcode=2007JGRE..112.6010M|doi-access=free|access-date=2022-04-01|archive-date=2021-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210710214917/https://epic.awi.de/id/eprint/16592/1/Mor2007e.pdf}}</ref>和南半球的佩纽斯和安菲特里忒破火山口地区<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Lefort | first1=A. | last2=Russell | first2=P.S. | last3=Thomas | first3=N. | title=Scalloped terrains in the Peneus and Amphitrites Paterae region of Mars as observed by HiRISE | journal=Icarus | volume=205 | issue=1 | page=259 | year=2010 | doi=10.1016/j.icarus.2009.06.005 | bibcode = 2010Icar..205..259L }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |last1= Zanetti |first1= M. |last2= Hiesinger |first2= H. |last3= Reiss |first3= D. |last4= Hauber |first4= E. |last5= Neukum |first5= G. |year= 2009 |url= http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2009/pdf/2178.pdf |title= Scalloped Depression Development on Malea Planum and the Southern Wall of the Hellas Basin, Mars |volume= 40 |journal= Lunar and Planetary Science |at= p. 2178, abstract 2178 |bibcode= 2009LPI....40.2178Z |access-date= 2022-04-01 |archive-date= 2016-06-16 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160616204734/http://www.lpi.usra.edu/meetings/lpsc2009/pdf/2178.pdf }}</ref>尤为突出。这种地形由带[[扇贝|扇贝]]或[[莲|荷叶]]状边缘、无隆起边垒的低浅洼地构成，通常称为扇形洼地或简称贝状。扇形洼地可能孤立，也可能聚集，有时似乎会合并在一起。一处典型的扇形洼地显示出一侧面向赤道的缓坡和另一侧面向极地的陡坡，这种不对称地形可能是因[[日照|日照]]差异所造成。扇形洼地被认为是[[升华|升华]]造成的地下物质（可能是间隙冰）流失而形成，这一过程至今可能仍在发生<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_007173_2245|title=HiRISE | Scallops and Polygons in the Utopia Planitia (PSP_007173_2245)|website=hirise.lpl.arizona.edu|access-date=2022-04-01|archive-date=2022-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220414181226/https://hirise.lpl.arizona.edu/PSP_007173_2245}}</ref>。

